snippet.title: Sentou Yousei Yukikaze: Yousei No Mau Sora (JPN) | Mission 1
snippet.description:
Starting now is the playthrough of the Yukikaze video game that was released exclusively in Japan (hence no English dialogue) in 2003 for the Xbox and in 2004 for Windows.
You can find the complete playthrough playlist here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLvnl04mTlSUgNikVyjwvIsOjh7S8bQjWa

Also check this playthrough for all my Yukikaze videos:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLvnl04mTlSUhiuk7-p8NYXZHQghQw5tXX
